<h1>
    Overview
</h1>
<p>
    An <a href="https://github.com/limpygnome/Portable-Postgres">open source</a> Windows application allowing for
    Postgres (PostgreSQL) to be portable, for development purposes.
</p>

<h1>
    Features
</h1>
<ul>
    <li>Automated download, install and setup of Postgres.</li>
    <li>Automatic launch.</li>
    <li>Automatic setup of pgAdmin database profile.</li>
    <li>Launches psql command window with connection info and current directory.</li>
    <li>Detection of runtime issues, such as multiple instances of Postgres running and port binding.</li>
    <li>Wipe and reinstall within a few clicks, useful for development.</li>
</ul>

